name: $execution
description: Executes code exported as a string from the specified file

name: $jsonAssign
description: Combines multiple JSON objects into a single JSON object

name: $append
description: Appends items into the last of list

args.name: sourcesToAppend
args.description: The source or target of items to be inserted

name: $delete
description: Deletes a key from an object or context

args.name: propertyKey
args.description: The name of the property or key of object

name: $deserialize
description: Deserializes a serialized input into an object

args.name: input
args.description: The input that is to be deserialized

args.name: deserializer
args.description: A deserializer instance or name of a registered service

name: $serialize
description: Serializes an object into a serializer

args.name: object
args.description: The object that is to be serialized

args.name: serializer
args.description: A serializer instance or name of a registered service

name: $requireCache
description: Deletes a module from the cache or reloads it (including dependencies)
